OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Fwill continue to bring showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain overnight, and a
OL,8,Fmixture of low cloud and fog leading
OL,9,Fto poor conditions, particularly over
OL,10,Fthe hills. Staying frost free under
OL,11,Fthe blanket of cloud.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,14,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain during
OL,15,Fthe morning. Skies will brighten a
OL,16,Flittle across eastern counties later
OL,17,Fon with some hazy spells of sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
